ay  this will not change the spreadsheet on the web  This first invoice covers the time from when you received the printer through November 28  2012  The next invoice will be from the period beginning November 28 through December 31  Subsequent invoices will be on a monthly basis  The data is sorted first by Department then GL   general Ledger number  Sub totals are by GL  If you have any questions regarding the Managed Printer Copier Service program please call Col  Hopkins at 7341  or email hopkinstf vmi edu  2013 03 01   Jan 2013 usage 2013 02 14a   Dec 2012 usage 2013 01 17b   Nov 2012 usage up to Previous 1 2 3 4 VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 